  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a small bowl, mix together coriander powder, cumin powder, garam masala, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Toss the halved cherry tomatoes with the spice blend until evenly coated.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the tomatoes and mix until well combined.",
    "Transfer the tomatoes to a baking dish and roast for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the tomatoes from the oven and sprinkle with cured lemon.",
    "Return the tomatoes to the oven and roast for an additional 10-12 minutes, or until caramelized.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve warm."
